Kill-bittorent
=====
Purpose: a simple app that will kill the offical BitTorrent program when it refuses to quit or is not closing fast enough.

The code is easily tweaked to target any program you may want a kill switch for. Simple change 'bittorrent' line in the code
    property program : "bittorrent" --search for this keyword and tell the program to shutdown now!


Requirements: 
=====
Mac OS X and AppleScript Editor to compile.

Released: 
=====
under the GPL 3+
